divs: Sighting DetailsI was standing outside my job at around 0555HRS having a cigarette and just staring at the stars, when I spotted two objects flying in unison. At first I thought it was birds but the object had no visible wings. Also, I then thought it might have been an airplane but I the object had no lights.
